{
  "stem": "3928.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wouldn't want to set a date or anything because I am not sure when I heard it, you know, or where I heard it, but I know I remember this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, I heard it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to me it was a big influence, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- the American movies with my childhood was a tremendous influence, you know, because I've seen there were a way-- I know it was a make-believe world, but when we're young, you know, a make-believe world is a real world for you.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when you see all the Andy Hardy movies, you know, and you see all the cowboy movies, and all the good movies, you know, was made in-- in Hollywood, I had-- I had a feeling that I-- someday, I going to work there.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I am going to be a cinematographer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I became one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I became a video-- videographer-- afterwards, which I hate, you know, because I love to work with films.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was my first love, you know, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- I felt-- actually, I almost left the country after I came here in 1951 for one, simple reason.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A-- no-- I went to a German club one time in-- in Pittsburgh, just to see what's going on, you know, and went to Hungarian club because you're new here.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You want to find out certain things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's a German man was there who admitted proudly that he was in the German army, and he fought the Americans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I told him, how did you come to this country?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, hell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, I told them-- I told them I was drafted, and everything, and they checked me out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I am right here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what bugged me the most is this.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
